description: Seattle's only mobile Taiyaki shop is on the streets and serving up some fantastic fish-shaped treats! BeanFish is bringing a fun new look to the food truck scene, with their traditional Japanese fish-shaped waffles made right before your eyes from the freshest ingredients and homemade waffle batter. With a variety of fillings to satisfy your sweet and savory cravings, BeanFish has something for everyone!
name: BeanFish
